'''[[destructive]] [[distillation]]'''
#{{chemistry}} the [[heating]] of a material, such as [[coal]] or [[wood]], in an [[inert]] [[atmosphere]], at a high [[temperature]] such as to cause [[decomposition]]; the [[principal]] [[product]]s include [[oil]]s and [[tar]]s from which many useful [[organic]] [[compound]]s may be obtained; [[town gas]] and [[coke]] were obtained in this way